}   Dear Amiga Inc

}   I am interested by the AACE, AmigaDE Player, or whatever else DE program player, 
}but I would just tell that the DEPlayer is too expansive, and should be provided
}for free.

}   If Amiga Inc provides the Player for free, I assume you I will make the effort 
}to buy 1 game (or more) just after having the DEPlayer ready, and will do my best 
}to talk about AmigaDE around the world, will pass the player to every personns in 
}my office, and will even help them installing those games ;)

}   So please, provides us the player for free, we will to the rest.

